# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [1.0.0] - Jan, 24, 2020
### Added
- Dockerfile
- Change log
- Readme
- Archives config
- Nginx 1.17.8
- PHP-FPM 7.4
- HTML Welcome Nginx

## [1.0.1] - Jan, 24, 2020
### Added
- Dockerfile Label Version and Company

### Fixed
- Adapting a writing pattern in the CHANGELOG.

### Remove
- Buld Status in READNE.md

## [1.0.2] - May, 29, 2020
### Added
- Support user and group www-data

## [1.0.3] - Jun, 03, 2020
### Update
- Versions Nginx and Composer
### Fixed
- Support a User www-data in /var/www/
## [1.0.4] - Jun, 03, 2020
### Added
- Adding support ACL HTTP authentication
## [1.0.5] - Jun, 03, 2020
### Fixed
- Fixer memory_zone in Nginx
## [1.0.6] - Jul, 02, 2020
### Added
- Adding modules mcrypt and gmp
## [1.0.7] - Jul, 23, 2020
### Added
- Added to required WordPress extensions
## [1.0.8] - May, 12, 2021
### Update
- Upgrade version PHP and Composer
- Clean packages install
- Change from image debian
- Update READNE